<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="es">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Sugerir Pregunta - Preguntame</title>
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.3/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }

        body {
            min-height: 100vh;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%);
            font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, Oxygen, Ubuntu, Cantarell, sans-serif;
            padding: 0;
            margin: 0;
        }

        .container-sugerir {
            max-width: 700px;
            margin: 100px auto;
            padding: 0 1rem 2rem;
        }

        .header-card {
            background: white;
            border-radius: 20px;
            padding: 2rem;
            margin-bottom: 2rem;
            box-shadow: 0 8px 32px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            text-align: center;
        }

        .header-card h1 {
            color: #667eea;
            font-size: 2rem;
            font-weight: bold;
            margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
        }

        .subtitle {
            color: #666;
            font-size: 1.1rem;
            margin: 0;
        }

        .form-card {
            background: white;
            border-radius: 20px;
            padding: 2.5rem;
            box-shadow: 0 8px 32px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }

        .form-label {
            font-weight: 600;
            color: #333;
            margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
            font-size: 1rem;
        }

        .form-control,
        .form-select {
            border: 2px solid #e0e0e0;
            border-radius: 12px;
            padding: 0.75rem 1rem;
            font-size: 1rem;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
        }

        .form-control:focus,
        .form-select:focus {
            border-color: #667eea;
            box-shadow: 0 0 0 0.2rem rgba(102, 126, 234, 0.25);
            outline: none;
        }

        .respuestas-section {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea15 0%, #764ba215 100%);
            border-radius: 15px;
            padding: 1.5rem;
            margin: 1.5rem 0;
        }

        .respuestas-section h5 {
            color: #667eea;
            font-weight: bold;
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
            font-size: 1.1rem;
        }

        .respuesta-input {
            position: relative;
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
        }

        .respuesta-input:last-child {
            margin-bottom: 0;
        }

        .respuesta-input input {
            padding-left: 3rem;
        }

        .respuesta-label {
            position: absolute;
            left: 1rem;
            top: 50%;
            transform: translateY(-50%);
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%);
            color: white;
            border-radius: 8px;
            padding: 0.25rem 0.5rem;
            font-size: 0.85rem;
            font-weight: bold;
            z-index: 1;
        }

        .botones-container {
            display: flex;
            gap: 1rem;
            margin-top: 2rem;
        }

        .btn {
            flex: 1;
            padding: 0.9rem 1.5rem;
            font-size: 1.05rem;
            font-weight: 600;
            border: none;
            border-radius: 15px;
            cursor: pointer;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
            text-decoration: none;
            display: inline-block;
        }

        .btn-success {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #10b981 0%, #059669 100%);
            color: white;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(16, 185, 129, 0.4);
        }

        .btn-success:hover {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #059669 0%, #047857 100%);
            transform: translateY(-2px);
            box-shadow: 0 6px 20px rgba(16, 185, 129, 0.5);
        }

        .btn-secondary {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #6b7280 0%, #4b5563 100%);
            color: white;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(107, 114, 128, 0.4);
        }

        .btn-secondary:hover {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #4b5563 0%, #374151 100%);
            transform: translateY(-2px);
            box-shadow: 0 6px 20px rgba(107, 114, 128, 0.5);
            color: white;
        }


        @media (max-width: 768px) {
            .form-card {
                padding: 1.5rem;
            }

            .header-card h1 {
                font-size: 1.6rem;
            }

            .subtitle {
                font-size: 1rem;
            }

            .botones-container {
                flex-direction: column;
            }

            .respuesta-input input {
                padding-left: 1rem;
                padding-top: 2.5rem;
            }

            .respuesta-label {
                left: 1rem;
                top: 1rem;
                transform: none;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

<div class="container-sugerir">
    <div class="header-card">
        <h1>üí° Sugerir una Pregunta</h1>
        <p class="subtitle">Propon√© tus preguntas y ayud√° a mejorar el juego</p>
    </div>

    <div class="form-card">
        <form action="http://localhost:8012/PROYECTO_PREGUNTADOS/PreguntaController/guardarSugerencia" method="POST">

            <div class="mb-4">
                <label class="form-label">Categor√≠a</label>
                <select name="categoria" class="form-select" required>
                    <option value="">Seleccion√° una categor√≠a</option>
                    <option value="HISTORIA">Historia</option>
                    <option value="DEPORTE">Deporte</option>
                    <option value="ARTE">Arte</option>
                    <option value="GEOGRAFIA">Geograf√≠a</option>
                    <option value="CIENCIA">Ciencia</option>
                </select>
            </div>

            <div class="mb-4">
                <label class="form-label">Pregunta</label>
                <input type="text" name="pregunta" class="form-control" placeholder="Escrib√≠ tu pregunta aqu√≠..." required>
            </div>

            <div class="respuestas-section">
                <h5>Respuestas posibles:</h5>
                {{#respuestas}}
                    <div class="respuesta-input">
                        <span class="respuesta-label">{{.}}</span>
                        <input type="text" name="respuestas[]" class="form-control" placeholder="Escrib√≠ la respuesta {{.}}" required>
                    </div>
                {{/respuestas}}
            </div>

            <div class="mb-4">
                <label class="form-label">Respuesta correcta</label>
                <select name="correcta" class="form-select" required>
                    <option value="">Seleccion√° cu√°l es la correcta</option>
                    <option value="0">Respuesta 1</option>
                    <option value="1">Respuesta 2</option>
                    <option value="2">Respuesta 3</option>
                    <option value="3">Respuesta 4</option>
                </select>
            </div>

            <div class="botones-container">
                <button type="submit" class="btn btn-success">Enviar sugerencia</button>
                <a href="http://localhost:8012/PROYECTO_PREGUNTADOS" class="btn btn-secondary">Volver a Home</a>
            </div>
        </form>
    </div>
</div>

<script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.3/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"></script>
</body>
</html>